From: Lukasz Majewski <lukma@denx.de>
Date: Sat, 21 Oct 2017 00:18:37 +0200
Subject: drm/panel: simple: Add Mitsubishi AA070MC01 panel support
Git-commit: 65c766cad8f81a65790580576a50abd21e3dea44
Patch-mainline: v4.16-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

The Mitsubishi AA070MC01 is a 7.0" WVGA (800x480) TFT panel working in
8 bit ISP mode (pin 19 "mode" HIGH for 20 pin TFT connector).

Signed-off-by: Lukasz Majewski <lukma@denx.de>
